  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1163387/" class="title-link">详细、全面的阿拉伯通史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1163387"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/abing/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1404017-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/abing/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">abing</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-06-03"
      class="main-meta">2007-06-03 22:08:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1163387_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      阿拉伯之历史书大都从穆罕穆德说起，终于阿拔斯王朝。但此书却不同，从公元前开始记述，专门有数章介绍伊斯兰教之前的阿拉伯社会，对于我们了解伊斯兰教兴起的社会历史渊源较有帮助。而且，该书以较多的篇幅记述了此外阿拔斯王朝之后的那段历史，对十字军那段历史也专辟章...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1163387/#comments">(13回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            商务印书馆1979版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1163387_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1163387_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



